dct_title_s: Topographic map of the island of Molokai, Hawaii
dct_description_sm: surveyed by the U.S. Geological survey in cooperation with the Territory of Hawaii.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
Includes location map: The Hawaiian Islands.
"A.O. Burkland, Topographic Engineer in charge ; topography by F.A. Danforth and M.J. Gleissner ; surveyed in 1921-22."
